name: Tempo with 30sec spike #1
description:
Steady Tempo efforts on their own are effective training. But by incorporating 30-second high-intensity efforts into them, you will improve your body's ability to work aerobically for long periods. Today's sessions consists of 2 x 12-minute Tempo efforts with a 30-second surge every 3.5 minutes.
